# 🌤️ WeatherForecastApp

A modern Android weather app built with **Kotlin**, **Jetpack Compose**, and **Clean Architecture**.
This project showcases best practices in **modular design**, **MVVM**, **dependency injection (Hilt)**, **unit testing (TDD)**, and **real-time localization & theme switching**.

---

## 📸 Screenshots

| Light Theme | Dark Theme |
|-------------|------------|
| ![Light](screenshots/light.png) | ![Dark](screenshots/dark.png) |

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🌐 Real-time weather forecast using the **[OpenWeatherMap API](https://openweathermap.org/)** (free tier)
- 🧱 Clean Architecture with modularization
- 🎨 Jetpack Compose UI with Material 3 design
- 🌙 Light/Dark theme switching in real-time
- 🌍 Language change (localization) without restarting the app
- 🔄 Reactive UI updates using `StateFlow` and `LiveData`
- 🔐 Dependency injection using Hilt
- ✅ Unit-tested domain and data layers
- 🧪 TDD-based development
- ⚙️ CI/CD ready (GitHub Actions configured)

